{%- comment -%}
  SBJ sub-category tiles — SKIMS "shop by category" row at the top of a collection.
  Auto-renders the right subcats per collection from the handle-keyed map below, so
  ONE instance on the default template serves every collection. Images are SKIMS's
  own category-tile assets (skims-sanity CDN); links are tag-filtered collection URLs.
{%- endcomment -%}

